import { styled } from '@material-ui/core/styles'
import NativeSelect from '@material-ui/core/Select'

const CustomSelect = styled(NativeSelect)({
    background: '#FFF',
    border: '1px solid #5656ef',
    borderRadius: 6,
    color: '#5656ef',
    padding: 15,
    minWidth: 150,
    maxWidth: 350
})

export default CustomSelect
